;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在加拿大自由党赢得三场关键特别选举后，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;马克·卡尼总理在加拿大赢得了&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/3E1h4rgcTrDZLfxxQzEx-qaV9jY1BuPwRuolO-D0xrEEvT3PsRIBPROLhutSU14NanVasp9kfeNf374_tb8mBNflaP4lRbKn3Jpu4cAYJkR33lHs3jVAbTIU2gkII76FC9PYQxoXSNrQTUyGuhAQnqK0y2rGVBGKbytjD2x_016w5B7PoinPq12zPqq3hzeehw5A2Al6H4gcC5OKU6_TkK8PUIJ4-_ET4xJuUALG0TP4g65ypUOAD-GzMfIu_BfKYy0vrxUVfufsqDdlVQyAhUkoDB3XGjqkKnRR3EH74mWN-uACmos97R94lgQSd8BpCFFWRBW_KBVsL8GHMN1YyOsm8OlgyGwnuVJcuE0Dl40AlH4vZzegyULbcd4WS-LIXW2mVmVVA2C4XFeEagncmPTtTJmzAoLZRT8CxiSa5QvR4qGZsAT1yCnCRiTRFoFpOJ7cq0AFEIWC7EaxFDg64WjvF2hMG9YiSZrinU783FtlZCYteiuWvQVYkBmhlY5TQoBONtm7rPggd-omGhOX99_B4S9U4rc/VcYhrLvn5iotBbY2eSVC0eiJtfIUEmob/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="卡尼赢得多数政府推动能源和贸易雄心"&gt;多数党政府&lt;/a&gt;，使他的政府能够更快地推进以扩大能源出口和减少对美国依赖为中心的经济议程。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;飙升的电力成本&lt;/strong&gt;给消费者带来了负担，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Lh3gL6Wgy5gZZslzGwdM9J_1dJkKWEdAaVqCh1j6bA4oLbGPtCk_ibxpp_eiVnoBylD6eErOJyOf1_eCyT3kWuriW-vUAwlFnKI6L1zB92N9saHZmDySn6y6HH1dP-JUyAeB5IBiDhLZ-PxTBNXvbdO-jmV5h2Lh5_DUWdSRPu7L8ml1nthGl2lBj58RyUy3dTqH515-Kzf7wXK5-wLTBkaXxxrDGvRWZ3AXVqvqmvzRQWsVAnDvv70nFRzjsx_0ZiEOkplHrGqJN6ZV1NqyyTsZHoM3L7iaCQ5yLNYGqPtvDn-J-D25-EWkxu5d8wY0dZKExS5xfLD4dguXq-Of8hQal-m3PnSSUftNQ8_yCXKUC7XH7YaERIIoRV54MyZoTFvYvhDU2Qf1OXO7YFYAdWAsypeDiR6glLTIUl7Wafhn4mzS-B_PryP2rLctjJ4ck18J0N0HDm4pyUBr3ck5Yw--c03PojHWmw/d_w_EDW29Nga9gU7-Wp5v6kG5DFkDlfq/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="飙升的电费在中期选举前激起选民的愤怒"&gt;激起了全美选民的愤怒&lt;/a&gt;，在11月中期选举之前，一度平凡的公用事业法案将成为美国政治的中心。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivEc6vy